{
  "texts": [
    "For all publications, cited articles were checked if the text suggested they might be relevant.",
    "For publications in which the user study was the main contribution, three sources were checked: other publications citing the publication, related publications and other publications of the main authors.",
    "Finally, a non-systematic search was conducted based on different short versions of the search string.",
    "To this end, subsets of the search terms were used (e.g., XAI, user study, saliency map) or the inclusion of specific task domains was forced by putting them in inverted commas (e.g., scene classification, scene recognition, object recognition, object detection, fine-grained).",
    "This non-systematic search was only performed with Google Scholar because this database does not correctly process some operators of search strings (i.e., ignoring parentheses)."
  ]
}